# Scoped to benchmarks/Dockerfile ONLY (BuildKit looks for <dockerfile>.dockerignore
# next to the Dockerfile before the root .dockerignore). Keeps this image's repo-root
# build context lean WITHOUT changing the root app image's context. The image installs
# deps fresh, so local installs/build artifacts must never ship.
node_modules
**/node_modules
.git
var
coverage
**/coverage
dist
**/dist
build
**/build
.next
**/.next
.svelte-kit
**/.svelte-kit
*.png
.playwright-mcp
.devcontainer
